  "texts": [
    "It not only enhances the training balance of the network but also improves the accuracy of detecting small targets, especially in the case of unbalanced category distribution.",
    "Context-Based InformationIn traffic scenarios, due to the limited information inherent to some objects, contextual cues play a crucial role in traffic scene object detection.",
    "Reference [49]introduced the Deep Identity Representation (Deep ID) network in 2014, which fused learned features (contextual information) with target features.",
    "Given the complexity of factors such as varying viewpoints, occlusions, and truncations that result in cars having different appearances or shapes, incorporating context information near the target is advantageous for distinguishing target objects in complex backgrounds.Research has shown that introducing attention mechanisms is one way to incorporate context information.",
    "In recent years, researchers have been inspired by human attention, which allows selective focus on key parts of received information."
